HEADWORD: Powder-posted
<hw>Pow"der-post`ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Affected with
dry rot; reduced to dust by rot. See <cref>Dry rot</cref>, under
<er>Dry</er>.</def> <mark>[U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

